com.sophia.item-and-weapon-pickup-system.name: com.sophia.item-and-weapon-pickup-system
com.sophia.item-and-weapon-pickup-system.description:
Tool to Set up Sophias Item and Weapon Pickup System. 
Includes one Sample Animator and various prefabs for a single manual setup. 
It is recommended to use the tool though as to generate virtually infinite Item Setups.
